snippet.title: THE CELEBRITIES DOUBLE WHO LOOK TOTALLY LIFE DIFFERENT WITH THEIR OF AMBER HEARD NATURAL HAIR
snippet.description:
Celebrities tend to be style chameleons by nature, changing their looks to suit their latest roles. This means that, somewhere along the way, the celeb sheds their original look. After making her film debut with a minor role in 2004's Friday Night Lights, Amber Heard has worked consistently in Hollywood to varying degrees of success. From bombs like Drive Angry to mega-blockbusters like Aquaman, this actress has carved out a wild onscreen career. However, you're more likely to know Heard from her personal life, which has become celebrity gossip fodder ever since the Texas beauty hit the world stage.
"Some people might get used to it, but not me. And it all seems to start with the hair! What don't stars do to their coifs? Coloring, cutting, straightening, curling — celebrities tweak their hair more than most people change their sheets #job-zc2lhr #Mandy Moore #Blair Waldorf #Hollywood #The Double (Dostoevsky novel) #Interview #Katherine García
